reviewText: Great to see the band in the early years again as I have been a fan since then. But this disc has audio problems. It does not sound very good at all. Not mentioned in the listing. Of course it is quite... old now. But it would have been nice to know first. I have bought many shows from "foreign" concerts & venues that looked & sounded great. This is not one of them.
Video is terrible, but it is a record of on of the band's early performances. For that it is worth having.
